      "content": "it's not just some \"process\" or something. it's like the color just went out of everything. i look at my stuff, my work, my life, and it all seems so stupidly pointless. like i'm just going through the motions for no reason. i just want the weight to stop. i just want to not feel this heavy anymore.",
